div.p:
Profits of state enterprises and organizations will total 69.6 in 1949 compared
                    39.3 [in] 1948, of this 41.4 from Industry vs 22.7, from Agriculture 1.6 vs 1.2;
                    Transport and Communications 12.4 vs 3.8; Trade and Procurement 6.7 vs 5.3;
                    other 7.3 vs 6.1.
